Class Asset

java.lang.Object
  play.db.jpa.JPABase
      play.db.jpa.GenericModel
          models.Asset
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, play.db.Model
@Entity
public class Asset
extends play.db.jpa.GenericModel

This class holds all xml-files Variants of originals are held in variant-counter, original is number 0 Name of xml-file is preserved as given when uploaded Name of assets should be on type Enunmeration of asset-type is kept in string due to db-restrinctions on jpa-enums
